{"tid":1942953,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"城巴就社交媒體流傳圖片作嚴正聲明","createTime":"2020-03-25T11:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T11:51:18.000Z","uid":164435,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ed0fb45e61ee9cbd7a704f6650efa250ac1cf5","tid":1942953,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:03:56.000Z","msg":"From新巴城巴Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NWFBCitybus/posts/667769837304319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNWFBCitybus%2Fposts%2F667769837304319&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=de9f83e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NWFBCitybus/posts/667769837304319</a><br />\n<br />\n城巴就社交媒體流傳圖片作嚴正聲明<br />\n<br />\n城巴留意今日在社交媒體流傳一張圖片，圖片中一名穿著城巴制服的車長配戴了疑似一條電子監察手帶。公司已立即展開調查，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>查證該圖片並非事實，相信曾被修改加入監察手帶</strong></span>。圖片中的車長近日並無離港，無需接受檢疫，身體狀態良好，體溫正常，今日亦有上班。<br />\n<br />\n在全城抗疫期間發放偽造圖片會引起公眾不必要恐慌，城巴強烈譴責此等不負責任行為。"},{"pid":"5b51bce278643075daeef47e33fc617acae1bab0","tid":1942953,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:05:01.000Z","msg":"其實咩事"},{"pid":"9cfcbe6fe5626ac126ed2f7694d181ba5f9c83c9","tid":1942953,"uid":95716,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:12:48.000Z","msg":"俾人惡搞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkbuschannel.com/2020/03/%e7%b6%b2%e5%82%b3%e3%80%8c%e6%89%8b%e5%b8%b6%e8%bb%8a%e9%95%b7%e3%80%8d%e7%85%a7-%e5%88%9d%e6%ad%a5%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af%e6%8c%87%e5%81%bd%e9%80%a0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkbuschannel.com%2F2020%2F03%2F%25e7%25b6%25b2%25e5%2582%25b3%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%2589%258b%25e5%25b8%25b6%25e8%25bb%258a%25e9%2595%25b7%25e3%2580%258d%25e7%2585%25a7-%25e5%2588%259d%25e6%25ad%25a5%25e6%25b6%2588%25e6%2581%25af%25e6%258c%2587%25e5%2581%25bd%25e9%2580%25a0%2F&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn%2BL6S